cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.NE

This paper deals with image analysis and clustering, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of supervised learning methods and dimensionality reduction techniques also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and statistical learning (cs.SD). Finally, the application of these techniques to predict solar activity may also fall under the category of natural language processing and computational biology (cs.NE).
